OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm but rather cloudy. Driest
OL,6,Fin eastern parts, with the best of any
OL,7,Fbrighter spells, while western parts
OL,8,Fprobably retaining thicker cloud
OL,9,Fthroughout, and seeing the bulk of any
OL,10,Fintermittent light rain and drizzle.
OL,11,FLight winds generally throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying warm but also
OL,14,Fremaining rather cloudy and damp, with
OL,15,Fspells of light rain and drizzle most
OL,16,Ffrequently affecting the west, but
OL,17,Fperhaps seen more widely towards dawn.
OL,18,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
