OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F166A1781585266
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy and damp during the
OL,6,Fmorning especially, but probably
OL,7,Ftending to become drier into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, with a greater chance of
OL,9,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Warm,
OL,10,Fwith light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FChangeable and often on the cloudy
OL,14,Fside through this period, with bands
OL,15,Fof rain making erratic progress
OL,16,Feastwards. Some warm sunny spells are
OL,17,Fstill expected, however, with
OL,18,Ftemperatures climbing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
